                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Egan</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-09-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 21, 1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Ex-President Balmaceda committed suicide in Argentine legation here 19th.
                    Everything tranquil.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Egan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
